OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with possibly
OL,6,Fsome light drizzle in places during
OL,7,Fthe morning. Cloud dissipating with
OL,8,Fsunny spells but breezy for most
OL,9,Fplaces by the afternoon. Feeling very
OL,10,Fwarm in the sunshine, cooler along the
OL,11,Fcoast with an onshore breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA clear evening for most.
OL,14,FOvernight, low cloud spreads inland
OL,15,Ffrom the North Sea, reaching many
OL,16,Fareas by dawn, though staying dry for
OL,17,Fmost. Remaining breezy, especially
OL,18,Falong the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
