OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FPatchy cloud affecting many
OL,6,Fin the morning, clear for others. A
OL,7,Fbright and sunny afternoon to follow
OL,8,Ffor most. Breezy, especially at
OL,9,Fcoasts. Above average temperatures,
OL,10,Fcooler by the sea.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,13,FCloudy at times, mainly mornings and
OL,14,Fovernight, with sunny spells each
OL,15,Fafternoon. Breezy, especially along
OL,16,Fthe coast. Very warm on Thursday,
OL,17,Fturning cooler by the weekend.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
